[Nouns] ingratitude, thanklessness, oblivion of benefits, unthankfulness.
"benefits forgot"; thankless task, thankless office.
[Verbs] be ungrateful; forget benefits; look a gift horse in the mouth.
[Adjectives] ungrateful, unmindful, unthankful; thankless, ingrate, wanting in gratitude, insensible of benefits.
forgotten; unacknowledged, unthanked, unrequited, unrewarded; ill-requited.
